--[[
    R6 Rig Builder Script - DUAL PART SYSTEM 🌪️
    Creates a controllable platform using dual-part replication
    
    DUAL-PART SYSTEM:
    - Client part: Full size (9.5x9.5x0.1), visible, UNANCHORED, local only
    - Server part: 0.001x size, invisible, replicated via F3X
    - Client part: Handles ALL physics/movement
    - Server part: Mirrors client part at 75Hz
    - NO network ownership conflicts!
    
    LASER EYES TOOL:
    - Stealth lasers: 0.001x size with 1000x mesh scale
    - Persistent server parts (pooled at 0, 2000, 0 when unequipped)
    - 30Hz visual updates, 10Hz destruction checks (optimized for performance)
    - Region3 spatial queries instead of GetDescendants (MUCH faster)
    - Max 10 parts destroyed per update to prevent lag
    - Destroys parts along laser path (excludes MainMap, characters, fake character)
    - Smart destruction: Won't destroy parts player is touching (except "Grass")
    - Laser ignores fake character (rigModel) in raycasts
    
    FLY TOOL:
    - Separate tool (auto-unequips after toggle)
    - PC: Press Q key to toggle fly
    - Mobile: Equip tool to toggle fly
    - Controls FAKE character (platform), NOT real player
    - BodyPosition + BodyGyro system
    - Camera-relative movement with WASD/joystick
    - Noclip enabled while flying on platform
    
    CHARACTER MOVEMENT:
    - Player character can move freely while controlling platform
    - No freezing or control conflicts
    - Platform control is independent from player movement
]]

